desc_short	-----								Super Cane Magic ZERO is a Comedy Arcade RPG with randomly generated dungeons. Fight solo or local co-op, get gear, eat bombs, crawl ridiculous dungeons and kill all the vegetables! There is also a full story mode coming later this year.							
